_sText: + ------------------------------------ + + *** ze_contamined-island *** + + ------------------------------------ + Lag free and beautifull, this map is a escape map for Zombie Mod. Contrary to the other maps, here you can NOT buy your weapons but you must found them in the map ! There is a lot of weapons so don't care about the avaible amo ^^ In the starting, you can go to the extraction point by the earth, the boat or the underground passage ! There is also some ambiance sounds (alarm, overwatch voice...). I make all what I can do to be the more realistic possible ! What's special : - Nuke with sound and fire - Secret Underground passage - Ambiance sounds - Can't buy weapons - Beautifull and lags free ~ Tactical video (coming soon) http//www.biokoxomodding.tk
